cu.explanation_en: Changing the GNB IPv4 address for NG-AMF to the same IP as the AMF (192.168.70.132) creates an IP address conflict, preventing the CU from binding to the NG-AMF interface.

du.explanation_en: Shifting the downlink absolute frequency point A by 1 unit causes frequency domain misalignment for the carrier, resulting in incorrect subcarrier mapping and signal distortion.
